rows.label: qst501901_msg0001
rows.name:
Um, hi there!
Would you like to buy some cookies?

rows.label: qst501901_msg0002
rows.name:
They're all handmade by people
from the camp here!

rows.label: qst501901_msg0003
rows.name:
We made them with honey, so
they're super sweet!

rows.label: qst501901_msg0004
rows.name:
Personally, I'd recommend having
one with a drink of Odifa!

rows.label: qst501901_msg0007
rows.name:
Oh, I'm so glad you actually
bought some.

rows.label: qst501901_msg0008
rows.name:
Sorry to bother you.
Maybe I'll see you again sometime!
